## [Package/Module] Structure

[CUSTOMIZE: Replace with your project's structure]

**For Java projects:**
```
src/main/java/com/example/[project]/
├── Main.java                           # Application entry point (XX lines)
├── [MainServlet/Controller].java       # HTTP request router
│
├── route/                              # Declarative routing system
│   ├── RouteRegistry.java              # YAML loader & pattern matcher
│   ├── Route.java                      # Route model
│   └── RouteDispatcher.java            # Handler dispatch
│
├── [processor or handlers]/            # Request processors
│   ├── [Interface].java                # Processor interface
│   ├── [Implementation1].java          # Specific handler
│   └── [Implementation2].java          # Another handler
│
├── storage/                            # File storage
│   ├── [Interface].java                # Storage strategy interface
│   ├── [Implementation].java           # Specific implementation
│   └── [Helper].java                   # Utilities
│
├── [datasource or db]/                 # Database layer
│   ├── [Strategy].java                 # Strategy pattern
│   └── [Implementation].java           # DB-specific code
│
├── model/                              # Domain models
│   ├── [Model1].java
│   └── [Model2].java
│
└── util/                               # Shared utilities
    ├── [Config].java                   # Configuration loader
    ├── [Json].java                     # JSON utilities
    └── [Logger].java                   # Logging wrapper
```

**For Rust projects:**
```
src/
├── main.rs                             # Application entry point
├── lib.rs                              # Library root (for tests)
│
├── routes/                             # HTTP handlers
│   ├── mod.rs                          # Router configuration
│   ├── [feature1].rs                   # Feature handlers
│   └── [feature2].rs                   # More handlers
│
├── services/                           # Business logic layer
│   ├── mod.rs
│   └── [feature]_service.rs            # Feature service
│
├── repositories/                       # Data access layer
│   ├── mod.rs
│   └── [feature]_repo.rs               # Data repository
│
├── models/                             # Domain models
│   ├── mod.rs
│   └── [model].rs                      # Serde models
│
├── middleware/                         # HTTP middleware
│   ├── mod.rs
│   ├── auth.rs                         # Authentication
│   └── logging.rs                      # Request logging
│
└── [utils or common]/                  # Shared utilities
    ├── mod.rs
    ├── config.rs                       # Config loader
    └── errors.rs                       # Error types
```

**For JavaScript/TypeScript projects:**
```
src/
├── index.[js|ts]                       # Application entry point
├── app.[js|ts]                         # Express/Fastify app setup
│
├── routes/                             # Route definitions
│   ├── index.[js|ts]                   # Router setup
│   └── [feature].routes.[js|ts]        # Feature routes
│
├── controllers/                        # Request handlers
│   └── [feature].controller.[js|ts]   # Feature controller
│
├── services/                           # Business logic
│   └── [feature].service.[js|ts]      # Feature service
│
├── models/                             # Data models
│   └── [model].[js|ts]                # Model definition
│
├── middleware/                         # Express middleware
│   ├── auth.[js|ts]                   # Authentication
│   └── errorHandler.[js|ts]           # Error handling
│
└── utils/                              # Utilities
    ├── config.[js|ts]                 # Configuration
    └── logger.[js|ts]                 # Logging
```

